{{ Feature 07: IF, IFNOT, ELSEIF, ELSE.

   Indentation defines controlled blocks.  The method returns a small checksum
   that changes if any branch condition is compiled incorrectly.
}}

PUB main() : r | x
    x := 7

    IF x > 10
        r := 100
    ELSEIF x == 7
        r := 7
    ELSE
        r := -1

    IFNOT x == 0
        r += 30
